/ Special Instructions / Notes","value":"Your free-form notes, shown only when you've entered them."}]},{"heading":"Buttons and Actions","items":[{"label":"New RFQ","value":"Starts a new request to send to vendors."},{"label":"Save / Create RFQ","value":"Saves the request. Grayed out until the form is filled in correctly or while it's saving."},{"label":"Send to Vendors","value":"Lets you pick vendors to ask for a price. Available while the request is a Draft or Sent."},{"label":"Record Response","value":"Lets you enter a vendor's quote. Available while the request is Sent or Receiving."},{"label":"Award","value":"Picks a vendor's quote as the winner and creates a purchase order for them. Available only while the request can still be awarded and the quote has been received. Can't be undone."}]},{"heading":"What's Required","items":[{"label":"Part","value":"Required. Pick a part from the menu."},{"label":"Quantity","value":"Required. At least 1."},{"label":"Required Date","value":"Required."},{"label":"Response Deadline, Description, Special Instructions","value":"All optional."},{"label":"Record Response — Vendor","value":"Required. Every quote detail (price, lead time, minimum order, tooling cost, valid-until, notes) is optional."},{"label":"Create RFQ — Save grayed out when","value":"Something's missing or wrong, or a save is already running. Hover the Save button to see what's left to fix."}]},{"heading":"Request List Columns","items":[{"label":"RFQ #","value":"The request's number. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Part","value":"The part number. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Description","value":"The part description. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Qty","value":"How many you need. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Status","value":"Where the request stands, shown as a colored label: Draft (gray), Sent (blue), Receiving (teal), Evaluating (amber), Awarded (green), Cancelled (red), Expired (gray). You can sort or filter by it."},{"label":"Vendors","value":"How many vendors you asked. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Received","value":"How many vendors have replied. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Required","value":"The date you need the part by. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Deadline","value":"The date you asked vendors to reply by, or a dash when none is set. Click the header to sort."},{"label":"Created","value":"The date the request was created. Click the header to sort."}]}]}"""
